alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIB.name: alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIB
alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIB.contactinfo: Alvarion Ltd. Postal: 21a HaBarzel St. P.O. Box 13139 Tel-Aviv 69710 Israel Phone: +972 3 645 6262

publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxCount.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxCount
publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxCount.description: The maximum number of entries inside the publicAccessRetentionSessionTable. The maximum value for this is 250% the maximum number of users configured inside the product.

publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxTime.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxTime
publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxTime.description: The maximum number of seconds for an entry to remain in the table. When expired the session's state changes to Unassigned.

publicAccessRetentionSessionTable.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionTable
publicAccessRetentionSessionTable.description: A table containing information about existing or past authenticated user sessions.

publicAccessRetentionSessionEntry.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionEntry
publicAccessRetentionSessionEntry.description: Information about a particular authenticated user session. publicAccessRetentionSessionIndex - Uniquely identifies a session in the table.

publicAccessRetentionSessionIndex.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionIndex
publicAccessRetentionSessionIndex.description: Index of a session in the publicAccessRetentionSessionTable.

publicAccessRetentionSessionState.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionState
publicAccessRetentionSessionState.description: Indicates the current state of the user's session.

publicAccessRetentionSessionUserName.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionUserName
publicAccessRetentionSessionUserName.description: Indicates the last user's name used for RADIUS authentication.

publicAccessRetentionSessionStartTime.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionStartTime
publicAccessRetentionSessionStartTime.description: Indicates when this user session was started.

publicAccessRetentionSessionDuration.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionDuration
publicAccessRetentionSessionDuration.description: Indicates how long the user's session has been active. When this counter reaches its maximum value, it wraps around and starts increasing again from zero.

publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsSent.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsSent
publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsSent.description: Indicates the total number of IP packets sent by the user. When this counter reaches its maximum value, it wraps around and starts increasing again from zero.

publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsRecei.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsReceived
publicAccessRetentionSessionPacketsRecei.description: Indicates the total number of IP packets received by the user. When this counter reaches its maximum value, it wraps around and starts increasing again from zero.

publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesSent.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesSent
publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesSent.description: Indicates the total number of bytes sent by the user. When this counter reaches its maximum value, it wraps around and starts increasing again from zero.

publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesReceive.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesReceived
publicAccessRetentionSessionBytesReceive.description: Indicates the total number of bytes received by the user. When this counter reaches its maximum value, it wraps around and starts increasing again from zero.

publicAccessRetentionSessionSSID.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionSSID
publicAccessRetentionSessionSSID.description: Indicates the user's Access Point SSID (ONLY when Location-aware is enabled and properly configured). If this information is not available, a zero-length string will be returned.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsMaxCou.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsMaxCount
publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsMaxCou.description: Specifies the maximum number of periods to keep inside the table.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsDurati.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsDuration
publicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsDurati.description: Specifies the amount of time for a period of an entry inside the table. Changing the value will erase the table contents.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodTable.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodTable
publicAccessRetentionPeriodTable.description: A table containing statistics information about number of authentication user's sessions pending and terminated.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodEntry.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodEntry
publicAccessRetentionPeriodEntry.description: Statistics information about the number of authenticated user sessions in a given period of time.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodStartTime.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodStartTime
publicAccessRetentionPeriodStartTime.description: Indicates the start time for the statistical period. If zero, then the period doesn't contains valid information.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodStopTime.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodStopTime
publicAccessRetentionPeriodStopTime.description: Indicates the stop time for the statistical period. If zero, the period is not terminated yet.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodHighestSessio.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodHighestSessionCount
publicAccessRetentionPeriodHighestSessio.description: Indicates the highest number of simultaneous authenticated user sessions within this time period.

publicAccessRetentionPeriodTotalSessionC.name: publicAccessRetentionPeriodTotalSessionCount
publicAccessRetentionPeriodTotalSessionC.description: Indicates the total number of authenticated user's session within this time period.

publicAccessRetentionSessionMaxCountReac.name: publicAccessRetentionSessionMaxCountReachedTrap
publicAccessRetentionSessionMaxCountReac.description: This notification is sent whenever the number of session exceed the value of publicAccessRetentionSessionsMaxCount.

alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIBComplian.name: alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIBCompliance
alvarionPublicAccessRetentionMIBComplian.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Alvarion Public Access Retention MIB.

alvarionPublicAccessRetentionSessionsMIB.name: alvarionPublicAccessRetentionSessionsMIBGroup
alvarionPublicAccessRetentionSessionsMIB.description: A collection of objects providing the Public Access Retention Sessions MIB capability.

alvarionPublicAccessRetentionPeriodicSta.name: alvarionPublicAccessRetentionPeriodicStatsMIBGroup
alvarionPublicAccessRetentionPeriodicSta.description: A collection of objects providing the Public Access Retention PeriodicStats MIB capability.
